<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Circus Juggling Masterclass</title>
    <style>
        /* עיצוב רקע הקרקס - פסים אדומים ושחורים */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(
                135deg,
                #5a0000,
                #5a0000 50px,
                #1a1a1a 50px,
                #1a1a1a 100px
            );
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* עיצוב אפקט ה-Blur והזכוכית */
        .glass-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 40px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px); /* זה האפקט של הטשטוש */
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            border: 2px solid #ffd700; /* מסגרת זהב */
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #ffd700;
            font-size: 3em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px black;
        }

        p.subtitle {
            color: #ffcccb;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .step-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #ffd700;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ffd700;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        /* עיצוב רספונסיבי לסרטוני היוטיוב */
        .video-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* יחס 16:9 */
            height: 0;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        }

        .video-wrapper iframe {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="glass-container">
        <h1>Welcome to the Circus</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Learn the 3-Ball Cascade - The Ultimate Beginner Guide</p>

        <div class="step-card">
            <h2>Step 1: The One Ball Arc</h2>
            <p>Start simple. Throw one ball from your dominant hand to your other hand. The ball should reach eye level and follow a smooth, invisible arch. Keep your elbows relaxed at your sides.</p>
            <div class="video-wrapper">
                <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-GcmtuRhDeg" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
            <h2>Step 2: The Two Ball Exchange</h2>
            <p>Hold one ball in each hand. Toss the first ball. <strong>Wait</strong> until it reaches its highest point (the peak), and only then toss the second ball underneath it in an X pattern. Catch, catch.</p>
            <div class="video-wrapper">
                <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/p4_IUMS4yc8?start=35" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
            <h2>Step 3: The 3-Ball Cascade</h2>
            <p>Hold two balls in your dominant hand, and one in the other. Start by throwing from the hand with two balls. Keep repeating the exchange from Step 2: right, left, right, left. Welcome to the show!</p>
            <div class="video-wrapper">
                <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dCYDZDlcO6g" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
